snippet.title: Amber Heard sips wine and enjoys a sunny lunch with her | News Stories Today
snippet.description:
Amber Heard sips wine and enjoys a sunny lunch with her | News Stories Today.
Amber Heard sips wine as she enjoys a sunny outdoor lunch with pal... after making donation to children’s hospital

Amber Heard enjoyed a sunny Saturday with a friend in the Los Feliz neighborhood of Los Angeles, having a wine-filled lunch.

The 31-year-old actress was clad in a beige safari hat with a black top and blue jeans, with a black pattern scarf and a black leather purse. 

The fresh-faced film star rounded things out with black slip-on leather shoes, as she was snapped chowing down and later paying a valet parker to retrieve her automobile.
